<p>
<note n="0381001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0381001">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0381002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0381002">勤＝勸【宮】</note>
<note n="0381003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0381003">鉢＝盋【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0381004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0381004">酥＝蘇【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
